snippet.title: Zipp’s Café - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Love, betrayal, and coffee! Step into the world of Zipp's Café in this reveal trailer for the upcoming cozy café management sim game. Zipp's Café is a small and cozy café management sim where you not only have to make delicious coffees and dinners but also solve some problems around your customers.

Zipp's Café will be available on PC on November 15, 2023.

#ZippsCafe
